When Black Love meets Black Entrepreneurship and becomes Generational Wealth. We love to see it, @patepalo_nyc! 👏🏾 #BlackOwned⁠
⁠
“Our family may come from Trinidad and Guyana, but we’ve found a second home in the bold and delicious flavors of the Dominican Republic. At @patepalo_nyc - Pat’e Palo Bar and Grill, we’ve brought together the best of our worlds to create a unique and welcoming dining experience in Inwood, NYC. Come for the food, stay for the love, and help us continue to share this beautiful story. ❤️🍴”⁠
